title: CoinOPS 5 R26
description:
CoinOPS 5 R26 (Sunset)

Install instructions:

Requires the original CoinOPS 5 FULL release. Download here:  <a href="
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8952769/CoinOPS_5_-_Full_Original_Release" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8952769/CoinOPS_5_-_Full_Original_Release</a>

Simply FTP over to your CoinOPS directory on your Xbox console and overwrite any all matching files.

Added 50 Skin Themes
Added Skin Templates...in PSD and also PNG overlays to just put over any background

Added Support for 4x3 and Scaled screen sizes....4x3 fits to 4x3...scales the origonal aspect ratio
Added Support for more arcade games like hsf2a (a fav of mine can now play in the mame core and the final burn core....so you can have the best of both worlds...speed or scanlines etc) double wings and much more in prep for CoinOPS 6
Documentation tidy ups
